      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Public Land Job Creation Act of 2015</b></p> <p>This bill gives the Bureau of Land Management (BLM) 45 days to review a state BLM notice for submission to the Federal Register. If the review has not been completed: (1) the notice shall consider to be approved, and (2) the state BLM office shall immediately forward the notice to the Federal Register for publication. </p>]]></text>
